title: [1508521049] Perfect Roast Turkey (Part 2) - Gordon Ramsay
description:
Gordon prepares turkey roasted with lemon, parsley and garlic and kept moist with streaky bacon. Watch the first part here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I93nany8nQI 

The most delicious Christmas recipes, cooked up by the world's greatest chef at home, "Gordon Ramsay's Ultimate Christmas" will teach you everything you need to know to cook up the perfect Christmas.
